# Control Service Rules

Control plane for users, profiles, workflows, monitoring, scheduling.

## Scope
- User/profile/document/preference/policy CRUD
- Workflow orchestration endpoints
- Monitoring and admin endpoints
- Audit writes and notification triggers

## Do NOT
- Implement board-specific scraping
- Implement browser automation
- Hardcode downstream board behavior

## Conventions
- Tenant-aware route structure
- Typed Pydantic request/response schemas
- Use workflow engine for state transitions
- Publish commands to fetcher/applier via abstraction
